
```
$ mongod --sslMode requireSSL --sslPEMKeyFile /srv/pki/server.pem --sslCAFile /srv/pki/intermediate/certs/ca-chain.cert.pem --auth
```

```
$ mongo --ssl --sslCAFile /srv/pki/intermediate/certs/ca-chain.cert.pem --sslPEMKeyFile /srv/pki/client.pem --host localhost
> db.getSiblingDB("$external").auth({mechanism: "MONGODB-X509"})
```
